                <div class="panel">
                    <p>The National Credit Regulator (NCR) was established as the regulator under the National Credit Act 34 of 2005 (the Act) and is responsible for the regulation of the South African credit industry. </p>

                    <p>See: <a href="https://www.ncr.org.za/">https://www.ncr.org.za/</a>  for further information.</p>
